sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as App Shell
    participant Sync as SyncService
    participant DexieDB as IndexedDB (Dexie)
    participant Supabase as Supabase
    participant Router as React Router

    Note over User,Router: ===== 应用启动 + 同步 =====

    App->>Sync: fullSync()
    Sync->>DexieDB: 获取 last_sync_at
    Sync->>Supabase: SELECT * FROM cards WHERE updated_at > last_sync_at
    Supabase-->>Sync: 远程变更列表
    loop 逐条比对
        Sync->>DexieDB: 本地版本查询
        alt 远程更新
            Sync->>DexieDB: 覆盖本地 (synced=true)
        end
    end
    Sync->>DexieDB: WHERE synced = false
    loop 本地未同步
        Sync->>Supabase: UPSERT card + upload image
        Sync->>DexieDB: 标记 synced=true
    end
    Sync->>DexieDB: 更新 last_sync_at
    Sync-->>App: 同步完成

    Note over User,Router: ===== 导入图片 =====

    User->>Router: 进入牌组管理 (/decks)
    User->>Router: 点击"导入"
    Router->>Router: 打开 ImportModal

    User->>Router: 拖入 / 选择图片文件
    Router->>Router: 校验格式 + 生成缩略图

    User->>Router: 确认导入
    loop 每张图片
        Router->>Supabase: upload image → storage_path
        Router->>Router: 构建 Card (front_text = 文件名去扩展名)
        Router->>DexieDB: upsertCard(card, synced=false)
    end
    Router->>DexieDB: updateDeckCardCount()
    Router-->>User: 导入完成

    Note over User,Router: ===== 学习流程 =====

    User->>Router: 仪表盘点击"开始学习"
    Router->>Router: 导航到 /study/:deckId

    Router->>DexieDB: getDueCards(deckId)
    Router->>DexieDB: getNewCards(deckId, dailyLimit - dueCount)
    Router->>Router: 合并为学习队列

    loop 队列中每张卡片
        Router-->>User: 显示正面：楷体大号文字
        User->>Router: 点击卡片
        Router-->>User: 翻转动画 → 背面书法图片
        Router-->>User: 显示评分按钮

        User->>Router: 点击评分 (Again/Hard/Good/Easy)
        Router->>Router: SM2.calculate(rating, card)
        Router->>DexieDB: updateCard(新状态, synced=false)
        Router->>DexieDB: updateSessionStats()
        Router->>DexieDB: upsertDailyStats(today)
    end

    Router-->>User: 学习完成页

    Note over User,Router: ===== 后台同步 =====

    App->>Sync: startBackgroundSync()
    loop 每 30 秒 + 页面隐藏
        Sync->>Sync: pushLocal()
    end
